\c 33
\s Ukubusa kukaManase
\p
\v 1 UManase wayeleminyaka elitshumi lambili esiba yinkosi; wasebusa iminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu lanhlanu eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 21.1-9.\x*.
\v 2 Kodwa wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, njengamanyala ezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazixotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\v 3 Ngoba wabuya wakha indawo eziphakemeyo uyise uHezekhiya ayezidilizile, wamisela oBhali amalathi, wenza izixuku, wakhothamela ibutho lonke lamazulu, walikhonza.
\v 4 Wasesakha amalathi endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayithe ngayo: EJerusalema ibizo lami lizakuba khona phakade.
\v 5 Wasesakhela ibutho lonke lamazulu amalathi emagumeni womabili endlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 Yena wenza abantwana bakhe badabule emlilweni esihotsheni sendodana kaHinomu\x + Josh. 18.16.\x*; wasechasisa izibonakaliso, wenza imilingo, wenza ubuthakathi, wasebenza labalamadlozi labalumbayo. Wenza okubi kakhulu emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuyithukuthelisa\x + Dute. 18.10.\x*.
\v 7 Wasebeka isifanekiso esibaziweyo sesithombe ayesenzile endlini kaNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu owayethe ngayo kuDavida lakuSolomoni indodana yakhe: Kulindlu, leJerusalema engiyikhethe kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, ngizabeka ibizo lami kuze kube nininini\x + 33.15. Dute. 4.16.\x*.
\v 8 Kangisayikususa unyawo lukaIsrayeli luphume elizweni engalimisela oyihlo, kuphela uba bezananzelela ukwenza konke engibalaya khona, ngokomlayo wonke lezimiso lezimiselo ngesandla sikaMozisi.
\v 9 Ngakho uManase waduhisa uJuda labahlali beJerusalema, ukwenza okubi okwedlula izizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazichitha phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuManase lebantwini bakhe, kodwa kabalalelanga.
\v 11 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yabehlisela abaphathi bebutho inkosi yeAsiriya eyayilabo\x + Dute. 28.36.\x*; basebethumba uManase ngameva\x + 25.18.\x*, bambopha ngamaketane ethusi, bamusa eBhabhiloni\x + 2 Kho. 20.17.\x*.
\v 12 Kwathi esecindezelwe wancenga ubuso beN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 1 Kho. 13.6.\x*, wazithoba kakhulu phambi kukaNkulunkulu waboyise\x + 32.26. 33.19,23.\x*.
\v 13 Wasekhuleka kuye, njalo wancengeka ngaye, wezwa ukuncenga kwakhe, wambuyisela eJerusalema embusweni wakhe\x + 33.19. Gen. 25.21.\x*. Ngakho uManase wazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yiyo enguNkulunkulu\x + Dan. 4.25.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Lemva kwalokho wakha umduli ongaphandle komuzi kaDavida ngentshonalanga kweGihoni esihotsheni\x + 1 Kho. 1.33.\x*, kwaze kwaba sekungeneni kwesango lenhlanzi\x + Neh. 3.3. 12.39. Zef. 1.10.\x*, wabhoda iOfeli, wawenza waphakama kakhulu. Wabeka labaphathi bamabutho kuyo yonke imizi ebiyelweyo koJuda.
\v 15 Wasesusa onkulunkulu bezizweni\x + 33.3,5.\x* lesithombe endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lawo wonke amalathi ayewakhile entabeni yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, laseJerusalema, wakuphosela ngaphandle komuzi\x + 33.7.\x*.
\v 16 Wasesakha ilathi leN\nd kosi\nd*, wahlabela phezu kwalo iminikelo yokuthula leminikelo yokubonga. Wathi kuJuda kakhonze iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 29.31.\x*.
\v 17 Loba kunjalo abantu babelokhu behlaba endaweni eziphakemeyo, kuphela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wabo\x + 32.12.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaManase, lomkhuleko wakhe kuNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 33.13,19.\x*, lamazwi ababoni abawakhuluma kuye ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*, khangela, kusezindabeni zamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 21.2.\x*.
\v 19 Umkhuleko wakhe-ke\x + 33.13,19.\x*, lokuncenga kwakhe \add kuNkulunkulu\add*, lesono sakhe sonke, lesiphambeko sakhe\x + 33.19. Gen. 25.21.\x*, lezindawo akha kuzo indawo eziphakemeyo, njalo wamisa izixuku lezithombe ezibaziweyo\x + 33.3,7.\x*, engakazithobi\x + 32.26. 33.19,23.\x*, khangela, kubhaliwe emazwini ababoni\x + 2 Sam. 24.11.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UManase waselala laboyise; basebemngcwaba endlini yakhe. UAmoni indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Kho. 21.18.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaAmoni
\p
\v 21 UAmoni wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lambili esiba yinkosi; wasebusa iminyaka emibili eJerusalema\x + 33.25,2 Kho. 21.19-24.\x*.
\v 22 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwenza kukaManase uyise; ngoba uAmoni wahlabela zonke izithombe ezibaziweyo uManase uyise ayezenzile, wazikhonza\x + 33.7. 34.3,4, 7.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa kazithobanga phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njengokuzithoba kukaManase uyise\x + 33.12.\x*, kodwa uAmoni lo wandisa icala.
\v 24 Inceku zakhe zasezimenzela ugobe, zambulala endlini yakhe.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa abantu belizwe batshaya bonke labo ababenzele inkosi uAmoni ugobe; abantu belizwe basebebeka uJosiya indodana yakhe ukuba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.